data.description: Have it at all this remodeled, stylish Sexton Mountain/Murray Hill contemporary. The main level features an open, Great Room layout with abundant windows that bring in natural light and showcase territorial views and amazing sunsets. The spacious kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances and opens to the casual dining room. Upstairs includes a vaulted primary suite featuring a walk-in closet and remodeled bathroom with double sinks and walk-in shower. The upper level is completed with two additional bedrooms, an updated Jack and Jill bathroom plus bonus room; perfect for reading, homework, games and more. Engineered wood floors on all levels...no carpet! Impressive, oversized garage for your storage and gear needs. Ultra private back deck for relaxing or entertaining. Convenient to Murray Hill shops & amenities, Nike and more. Roof (2022) Newer Exterior Paint and Decks. Inquire about assumable loan terms.
